   * @notice  Accepts collateral from the bridge
   * @dev     This function will take all collateral and deposit it into maha
   *          The ZAI from the deposit will be sent to the lockbox to be wrapped into xZAI
   *          The xZAI will be burned so that the xZAI on the L2 can be unwrapped for ZAI later
   */
